            on the inner structure, designed for glass and small-ware in bars and prep stations. Common service:
            door gasket, door switch, fill solenoid, drain pump, wash pump rebuild. LA bar clusters in WeHo, DTLA,
            and Santa Monica run heavy LXeR populations for glassware.</p>
        </div>
